metadata.name: Nostalgia
metadata.description: This picture is from the Franklin Delano Roosevelt Memorial in Washington D. C. (fitting for this period of volatile current events), taken about 10 years ago. It was one of the first photos I've taken where I experimented with motion blur, my absolute favorite effect. It now also serves as a timestamp to look back on, for the early days of my NFT journey. Here's to the next 10 years of growth and beyond!
